我細個就係比個垃圾老師拖咗幾年，乜柒都學唔到，斷送我成個鋼琴生涯咁滯，到我認清事實既時候用咗好多時間先追到一部分<br />\n啟蒙老師先係最重要，未夠班真係唔好害人，賺來既都係陰質錢來的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aead174fde7e32e912b998fd95707a6f3e500db","tid":463772,"uid":71974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T15:41:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>八級真心你繼續學上去先好出黎教<br />\n而家八級唔值錢 起碼考番個ATCL或以上先好出黎教</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係諗住一路教學生 一路賺錢學上去<br />\n屋企唔係有錢 唔可能辭職去學琴 <br />\n做幼稚園辛苦到完全無私人時間<br />\n食完飯就夠鐘訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你連私人時間都冇仲點去教琴<br />\n唔好話教啦 你連自己都未搞掂<br />\n你咁樣出去真係誤人子弟<br />\n我自己就係細個比個8級大學生教<br />\n一教一拖咁就冇左5年時間<br />\n好彩比我遇到而家個鋼琴老師<br />\n將我由頭重新開始執過<br />\n用左6年時間考左個ATCL番黎<br />\n黎緊再去考LTCL"},{"pid":"485be7c79fdc1c69ef01b139e519ef7c9a364e76","tid":463772,"uid":83992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:07:09.000Z","msg":"想學 8 級仲好 唔洗咁貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  反正我咩都唔識 唔洗咁勁既老師 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/doitnow2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdoitnow2&d=JhSGDKJ8TmPruShCzyVNv0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=bb648abf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/doitnow2</a>"},{"pid":"962f7568a23ac33ddfc889d11b03b6f0084b7188","tid":463772,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T16:34:33.000Z","msg":"隻手指硬到好似打左石膏<br />\n24歲 有無機會學？"},{"pid":"173b3a92e14fbf37e08cdf254f0117e3b9a0d161","tid":463772,"uid":83354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T18:19:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得8級教乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個名做咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=